# Architecture

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 14 App Router (TypeScript strict) |
| Database | Supabase (PostgreSQL + PostGIS for geo queries) |
| Auth | Supabase Auth + BankID via Signicat/Criipto |
| Payments | Stripe Connect (platform fee model) + Vipps via Stripe Payment Element |
| Search | Typesense (geo-aware, synced from Supabase via webhooks) |
| i18n | next-intl |
| Email | Resend + React Email |
| Background jobs | Trigger.dev |
| File storage | Cloudflare R2 (S3-compatible) |
| Cache / rate limiting | Upstash Redis |
| Maps | Mapbox GL JS |
| Analytics | PostHog |
| Error monitoring | Sentry |
| Hosting | Vercel (app) + separate VPS for Typesense |

